00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
What if your screen could be more vibrant than ever?

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:05,200
Enter quantum dots.

3
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:11,200
Quantum dots are tiny semiconductor particles that can emit specific colors when light hits them.

4
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:15,200
This technology is revolutionizing displays, enhancing color accuracy and brightness.

5
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:16,800
Imagine movies that pop!

6
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:22,800
Studies show quantum dot displays can be up to 50% more efficient than traditional LEDs.

7
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:28,000
The clarity is stunning, but there are still challenges in production and longevity.

8
